@67   = ~Letter from Cirion~
@68   = ~I think we have located the item. If it is indeed as powerful as it is rumoured to be, the Countess will surely be pleased. Secure a base somewhere, and then come and meet us in the bowels of the city. Kill any who oppose you, but use restraint. Being discovered will only bring us more problems. Once we have the item, you can satiate your bloodlust to your heart's content.

Cirion
~
@69   = ~Chain Mail Bikini~
@70   = ~Prized by many males on Faerun, the humble chain mail bikini is now the stuff of legend. This one seems to be constructed of simply a few squares of chain mail and scraps of leather, providing little modesty and maximum cleavage potential.

(This item provides little to no actual protection, and you do wonder for a moment why Ribald would have something like this in stock... although maybe you could convince a certain person to give you a very private viewing...)~
@71   = ~Exquisite Ruby Ring~
@72   = ~This ring appears to have no other purpose than one of decoration. The ruby that adorns it is a deep crimson colour that almost matches the colour of Fade's eyes. It has no flaws and is beautifully cut, catching the light on every facet so it appears to glitter even when held still.

Wearable by:
Fade~
@73   = ~Engraved Ruby Ring~
@74   = ~This ring appears to have no other purpose than one of decoration. The ruby that adorns it is a deep crimson colour that almost matches the colour of Fade's eyes. It has no flaws and is beautifully cut, catching the light on every facet so it appears to glitter even when held still. There is now an inscription engraved on the inside of the ring that reads: "Dearest Fade, With Love Forever, <CHARNAME>."

Wearable by:
Fade~
@75   = ~This ring appears to have no other purpose than one of decoration. The ruby that adorns it is a deep crimson colour that almost matches the colour of Fade's eyes. It has no flaws and is beautifully cut, catching the light on every facet so it appears to glitter even when held still. There is now an inscription engraved on the inside of the ring that reads: "Yours always and forever, <CHARNAME>."

